@startuml
actor User
participant "WinForms GUI" as GUI
participant "Form" as Form
participant "Python/Exe" as Proc
participant "Temp files" as Temp

User -> GUI: Load image and select module
GUI -> Form: Forward input and parameters
Form -> Proc: Run script or exe
Proc -> Temp: Save output
Proc --> Form: Return status
Form -> GUI: Load output and display
GUI --> User: Review and save
@enduml
